1
04:05:27,688 --> 04:05:28,938
[SQUAWKING]

2
04:05:30,941 --> 04:05:32,818
The Eagles are coming.

3
04:06:20,196 --> 04:06:21,450
[COUGHING AND GASPING]

4
04:06:23,118 --> 04:06:23,910
Bilbo.

5
04:06:24,161 --> 04:06:26,121
Don't move. Don't move. Lie still.

6
04:06:27,789 --> 04:06:30,333
Oh. Mm. Mm.

7
04:06:30,709 --> 04:06:31,884
I'm glad you are here.

8
04:06:32,085 --> 04:06:33,628
- Shh, shh.
- Unh.

9
04:06:34,588 --> 04:06:36,381
I wish to part from you in friendship.

10
04:06:36,631 --> 04:06:39,621
No...
You are not going anywhere, Thorin.

11
04:06:39,843 --> 04:06:41,178
You're going to live.

12
04:06:41,636 --> 04:06:44,723
- I would take back
my words and my deeds at the Gate.

13
04:06:46,558 --> 04:06:48,977
You did what only a true friend would do.

14
04:06:50,437 --> 04:06:52,090
Forgive me.

15
04:06:54,232 --> 04:06:56,318
I was too blind to see it.

16
04:06:58,695 --> 04:07:00,238
I am so sorry...

17
04:07:01,615 --> 04:07:03,492
...that I have led you into such peril.

18
04:07:04,659 --> 04:07:07,412
No, I'm glad to have shared
in your perils, Thorin.

19
04:07:07,662 --> 04:07:08,955
Each and every one of them.

20
04:07:12,375 --> 04:07:15,337
It is far more than any Baggins deserves.

21
04:07:19,758 --> 04:07:21,008
Farewell...

22
04:07:21,885 --> 04:07:23,678
...Master Burglar.

23
04:07:25,013 --> 04:07:27,057
Go back to your books.

24
04:07:28,225 --> 04:07:30,227
And your armchair.

25
04:07:31,978 --> 04:07:33,897
Plant your trees.

26
04:07:34,564 --> 04:07:36,233
Watch them grow.

27
04:07:37,692 --> 04:07:38,985
[GROANS]

28
04:07:41,279 --> 04:07:43,031
If more people...

29
04:07:44,074 --> 04:07:45,700
...valued home...

30
04:07:45,951 --> 04:07:47,911
...above gold...

31
04:07:48,912 --> 04:07:52,499
...this world would be a merrier place.

32
04:07:54,626 --> 04:07:55,669
[GRUNTS]

33
04:07:56,169 --> 04:07:58,463
No. No, no, no. No.

34
04:07:58,713 --> 04:08:01,133
Thorin. Thorin, now don't you dare...

35
04:08:03,426 --> 04:08:04,553
Thorin.

36
04:08:10,517 --> 04:08:12,894
Thorin. Thorin, hold on.

37
04:08:13,145 --> 04:08:14,471
Hold on, please.

38
04:08:14,855 --> 04:08:16,190
The Eagles...

39
04:08:16,690 --> 04:08:18,900
The Eagles... The Eagles are here.

40
04:08:19,568 --> 04:08:20,735
Thorin?

41
04:08:23,947 --> 04:08:25,197
The Ea...

42
04:08:26,575 --> 04:08:28,577
[SOBBING]

